				<section>
					<h2>Correlation and Causation</h2>
                    <ul>
                        <li> <small>Correlation is not the same thing as causation.</small> </li>
                        <li class="fragment fade-in"> <small>Two things that occur often together can in fact not be causally related if there are unobserved variables.</small> </li>
                    </ul>
                    <svg width="700px" height="800px" viewBox="-40 0 800 100" class="fragment fade-in">
                          <defs>
